Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特是邪恶的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘必须被打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真的是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想认识更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去更多的地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想活得更像个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌她…到底做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人有事想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事希望你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于你的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们制造的新型高达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经离问世不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员使用的认证装置构造复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还未能完全破解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能知道那位少年生物信息的认证代码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想破解装置干什么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 我可以帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去给她 给露乌治病用！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？给我药的话我就帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有药物可以使那种病痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充其量延缓病情发展 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会吩咐人准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成认证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密码程序数据也回收完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你不要再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧？是吉欧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 我该如何感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉已经好点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会这么快见效的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得就是这么快！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的谢谢你 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么贵重的药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪儿搞到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了晚饭再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多坐会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次那些话别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后还会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里随时欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见 露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是第几天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着那孩子的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像罗米还活着一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你画得？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌有绘画的才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵！ 猜猜是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把吉欧来的事 写在日记上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还写了一点 未来的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和吉欧一起散步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在废山上眺望景色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去不了外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想 如果能这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想出去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服用着吉欧的药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去稍微走走应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 这是去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近我不太认识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个好地方带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日记上写的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生病以前经常去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是附近风景最漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.15,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如小道绵延般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:44.16,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿此时光长存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:50.90,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}听山丘上的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:56.88,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}诉说凄惨的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.99,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:09.12,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令世界绚丽多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:15.66,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让离别再多等片刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:21.41,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽情拥抱温馨时光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:28.78,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为你不再伤心落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:34.18,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我努力献上微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:40.89,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明明能做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:47.16,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}却被诚实的泪水揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:53.47,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初识生的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:12:01.61,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}试着低声说出「幸福…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球一定比这里更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日记上写的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 吉欧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来喽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去躺会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始 虽说不想让你再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想到 就算吃了药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌剩下的时间也不会太长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 正因为这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才想让她过得更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 不愧是维甘的隐身伞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的战舰残骸浑身是宝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到海盗大展身手的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们要找的宝藏是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑猎犬出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里出现敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 韦氏蒂安利用了隐形技术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄靠近过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他们竟然拥有我们的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你对付他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能避免损失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽 不许吉欧·明日野走出房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为夺回高达做好准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去营救吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 首先是找出吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-23区 严防官邸上空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门 开门啊！喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是感动的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来凑热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 没有多余的时间奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 你到底在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有话待会儿说 先上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去找高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会救你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这座第二月球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是亚修船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-3那边进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经入侵格纳库管理系统
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时听候吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早给你拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追！追！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:18:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须去给朋友送一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不看这是什么时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 回来 吉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌一定是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都多亏你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…什么也没为她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌自从遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了什么是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 你原来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 来屏幕显示的汇合地点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌把未来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的记忆 写在日记上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括很远的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天和吉欧一起去了公园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荡秋千 跷跷板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩什么都开心！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧今天感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到我照顾吉欧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像吉欧做的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直陪在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是吉欧的生日！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在生日卡上写道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧在身边 我就开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的病也一定会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 突破大门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吉欧在 世界也变得绚丽多姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我 终于和吉欧来到了地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这片和吉欧共同踏上的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 什么？
